            "textentryhtml":"Private collection, London, UK, purchased at a Paris flea market, by 2010; [purchased by Adire African Textiles, London, UK, ca. 2010]; purchased by the Princeton University Art Museum, Princeton, NJ, January 2020.",
            "remarks":"See Provenance Notes for additional, private provenance information. -PL, 11/6/2023\r\nRevised by Perrin Lathrop, 4/4/25"
